		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Kombucha</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Kombolcha_(disambiguation)" title="Kombolcha (disambiguation)">Kombolcha (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">For the Japanese squash, see <a href="/wiki/Kabocha" title="Kabocha">kabocha</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Kombucha_jar.jpg" class="image" title="A Kombucha culture fermenting in a jar"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Kombucha_jar.jpg/200px-Kombucha_jar.jpg" width="200" height="227" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Kombucha_jar.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
A Kombucha culture fermenting in a jar</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Kombucha</b> is the Western name for sweetened tea or <a href="/wiki/Tisane" title="Tisane" class="mw-redirect">tisane</a> that has been <a href="/wiki/Fermentation_(food)" title="Fermentation (food)">fermented</a> using a macroscopic solid mass of microorganisms called a "kombucha colony".<br /></p>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="/wiki/File:300ml_glass_of_kombucha_with_ice.png" class="image" title="A glass of kombucha made from black tea"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/300ml_glass_of_kombucha_with_ice.png/150px-300ml_glass_of_kombucha_with_ice.png" width="150" height="235" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:300ml_glass_of_kombucha_with_ice.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
A glass of kombucha made from black tea</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Kombucha_Mature.jpg" class="image" title="Mature Kombucha yields a new batch quickly."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/48/Kombucha_Mature.jpg/150px-Kombucha_Mature.jpg" width="150" height="222" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Kombucha_Mature.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Mature Kombucha yields a new batch quickly.</div>
</div>
</div>
