0%2990083-A&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/2208084&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fentrez%2Fquery.fcgi%3Fcmd%3DRetrieve%26db%3DPubMed%26list_uids%3D2208084%26dopt%3DAbstract&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kombucha"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFPhanJane_Estell.2C_Geoffrey_Duggin.2C_Ian_Beer.2C_Diane_Smith_and_Mark_J_Ferson1998">Phan, Tri Giang; Jane Estell, Geoffrey Duggin, Ian Beer, Diane Smith and Mark J Ferson (1998). "<a href="http://mja.com.au/public/issues/xmas98/phan/phan.html" class="external text" title="http://mja.com.au/public/issues/xmas98/phan/phan.html" rel="nofollow">Lead poisoning from drinking Kombucha tea brewed in a ceramic pot</a>". <i>The Medical Journal of Australia</i> (Australasian Medical Publishing Company) (169): 644–646<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://mja.com.au/public/issues/xmas98/phan/phan.html" class="external free" title="http://mja.com.au/public/issues/xmas98/phan/phan.html" rel="nofollow">http://mja.com.au/public/issues/xmas98/phan/phan.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Lead+poisoning+from+drinking+Kombucha+tea+brewed+in+a+ceramic+pot&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Medical+Journal+of+Australia&amp;rft.aulast=Phan&amp;rft.aufirst=Tri+Giang&amp;rft.au=Phan%2C+Tri+Giang&amp;rft.au=Jane+Estell%2C+Geoffrey+Duggin%2C+Ian+Beer%2C+Diane+Smith+and+Mark+J+Ferson&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.issue=169&amp;rft.pages=644%E2%80%93646&amp;rft.pub=Australasian+Medical+Publishing+Company&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmja.com.au%2Fpublic%2Fissues%2Fxmas98%2Fphan%2Fphan.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kombucha"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-komucha_yeasts-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-komucha_yeasts_14-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFMAYSER_P._.281.29_.3B_FROMME_S._.3B_LEITZMANN_C._.3B_GR.C3.9CNDER_K.1998">MAYSER P. (1)&#160;; FROMME S.&#160;; LEITZMANN C.&#160;; GRÜNDER K. (1998). <a href="http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&amp;cpsidt=2897443" class="external text" title="http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&amp;cpsidt=2897443" rel="nofollow">"The yeast spectrum of Kombucha"</a>. Blackwell, Berlin, ALLEMAGNE<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&amp;cpsidt=2897443" class="external free" title="http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&amp;cpsidt=2897443" rel="nofollow">http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&amp;cpsidt=2897443</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+yeast+spectrum+of+Kombucha&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=MAYSER+P.+%281%29+%3B+FROMME+S.+%3B+LEITZMANN+C.+%3B+GR%C3%9CNDER+K.&amp;rft.au=MAYSER+P.+%281%29+%3B+FROMME+S.+%3B+LEITZMANN+C.+%3B+GR%C3%9CNDER+K.&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.pub=Blackwell%2C+Berlin%2C+ALLEMAGNE&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcat.inist.fr%2F%3FaModele%3DafficheN%26cpsidt%3D2897443&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kombucha"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
